makarov-desc = Cho? Gun is gun comrade. Uses 9mm ammo.
mosin-desc = Enemies at the airlock. Uses .44 magnum ammo.
ppsh-desc = The legendary PPSH 59. Inaccurate as hell, but delivers it. Uses 9mm ammo.

# Wearables
