# Bundles
combat-bundle = Combat Bundle
combat-bundle-desc = A basic set of armor, clothes and a makarov with extra magazines and a box. Fight, comrade!

combat-bundle-eva = Combat EVA Bundle
combat-bundle-eva-desc = A simple USSP EVA suit with oxygen, clothes and a makarov with extra magazines and a box. Fight in space, comrade!

combat-bundle-advanced = Advanced Combat Bundle
combat-bundle-advanced-desc = Has all a comrade needs! Comes with a mask, combat fatigues, boots, chest rig and a makarov & mosin combo, with extra magazines and a box.

combat-bundle-eva-advanced = Hardsuit Combat Bundle
combat-bundle-eva-advanced-desc = The very best the USSP has to offer! Comes with a marine hardsuit with oxygen, mask, combat fatigues, boots, chest rig and Stechkin & AK47 with extra magazines and a box.

commandant-crate-name = Commandant Crate
commandant-crate-desc = Lead the masses to victory, comrade!

supplies-crate-name = Supply Crate
supplies-crate-desc = Holds enough ammunition, medical supplies and food to bolster the Revolution while waiting on Rift supplies.